data.description: Top of the hill in Jette Lake! Walking into the front door brings you to a great open concept living space. A partially covered, wrap-around deck will beckon you to enjoy the serenity of the land with peek-a-boo views of Flathead Lake. 2 beds and 1 bathroom round out the main level. The lower level includes a large family room with a walk out door leading to the patio. There is also a bonus room which could easily be turned into a bedroom. Nestled on over 5 acres of land with great rolling topography. There is a fenced in area for your furry friends, and a large yard area that surrounds the house with a 12x18 barn style shed, 12x18 slab and a 6x7 shed. An oversized 2 car garage with plenty of extra space for your hobbies and additional outbuildings for storage. Take advantage of the homeowners only Jette Lake, which is stocked with fish and has a great day use site for a quick getaway. More pictures to come next week! Call Ty Heaton at 406-499-8209 or your real estate professional.
